thread.title_full: Lauryn Rose reviewed by Gwen Lawson

author: Gwen Lawson
title: Gwen Lawson
text: I ordered my chain very late on a Wednesday night but had it on Friday morning the packaging alone was beautiful, so much so that when I order again and I will order again I can have it sent direct as a gift so happy with the service, quality of my necklace, the packaging etc thrilled that I've found this little gem!!!
